        <item>
            <title>不再推出新一代 Fitbit 智能手表     Google：未来将由 Pixel Watch 取代</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/no-more-fitbit-watches/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=no-more-fitbit-watches</link>
